# CODEOWNERS - Mandatory Review Assignments
# This file enforces human-in-the-loop governance for all changes

# Default: All code requires architect team review
* @team-architects

# Source code requires lead developer review
/src/ @lead-developer @team-architects

# Security-sensitive files require security team
/src/validationMiddleware.js @security-team @lead-developer
/.github/workflows/ @security-team @devops-lead

# Tests require quality lead review
/tests/ @quality-lead @lead-developer

# Governance docs require program lead review
/docs/ @program-lead @team-architects

# CI/CD and infrastructure changes require DevOps lead
/.github/ @devops-lead @security-team

# Package dependencies require security review
package.json @security-team @lead-developer
package-lock.json @security-team

# Copilot instructions require SME review
/.github/copilot-instructions.md @copilot-sme @team-architects
